-#
  Presents a confirmation message before attempting to remove an administrator from a tournament

  Expects the following instance variavles to be defined

  @param [TournamentAdmin] tournament_admin The relationship that will be destroyed
#removeAdmin
  .modal-header
    %h2.modal-title= t('tournament_admin.destroy')
  .modal-body
    = form_tag tournament_admin_path(@tournament_admin), method: :delete do
      .form-horizontal
        .form-group
          %label.col-sm-12= t('tournament_admin.confirm_remove', admin_name: @tournament_admin.user.name)
          = render 'public/modal_form_buttons'
